Package: port
Type: Package
Title: Positivity Regression Trees Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Arthur Chatton
Maintainer: Arthur Chatton <arthur.chatton@umontreal.ca>
Description: PoRT is an entire framework for checking the causal assumption of posivity.
    Positivity checking for cross-sectional settings and longitudinal studies are implemented currently.
    References: Danelian et al. (2023; doi: 10.1515/jci-2022-0032) and Chatton et al. (2024; doi: 10.48550/arXiv.2412.10245).
